dct_description_sm: Taken from atlas--attached leaf is pages 183-184, and includes illustration and text (letter regarding treatment of the Empress Dowager by a Dr. Cochrane and his Chinese colleage, Mr. Li, and also text regarding the building up of schools and churches in South Africa), dated 1908.
Inset map: "Southeast England on same scale."
Shows railways, steamer routes, cities and regions, countries distinguished by coloring.
